---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '@components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro'
const lastUpdated = 'April 17, 2026'
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="MLEbotics terms of service — rules and conditions for using our website and products.">
  <Header />
  <main id="main-content">
    <div class="container legal">
      <div class="legal__header">
        <p class="tag">Legal</p>
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="legal__meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal__body">
        <p>These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your access to and use of MLEbotics websites, products, and services (collectively "Services"). By accessing our Services, you agree to be bound by these Terms.</p>

        <h2>1. Use of Services</h2>
        <p>You may use our Services for lawful purposes only. You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations.</li>
          <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, decompile, or hack our Services.</li>
          <li>Use our Services to transmit spam, malware, or harmful content.</li>
          <li>Impersonate MLEbotics or any other person or entity.</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the integrity or performance of our Services.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content, code, branding, and materials on this website are owned by or licensed to MLEbotics. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our express written permission.</p>
        <p>Open-source components of our software are licensed under their respective licenses as indicated in the source repositories.</p>

        <h2>3. User Content</h2>
        <p>If you submit content to our Services (e.g., community chat messages), you grant MLEbotics a non-exclusive, royalty-free license to use, display, and distribute that content in connection with our Services. You retain ownership of your content.</p>
        <p>You are responsible for any content you submit and agree it does not violate any third-party rights.</p>

        <h2>4. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>Our Services are provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement.</p>
        <p>We do not warrant that our Services will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or other harmful components.</p>

        <h2>5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, MLEbotics shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits or revenues, arising from your use of our Services.</p>

        <h2>6. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our Services may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites.</p>

        <h2>7. Modifications to Services</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of our Services at any time without notice. We will not be liable to you or any third party for any modification, suspension, or discontinuation.</p>

        <h2>8. Termination</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to terminate or suspend your access to our Services at our sole discretion, without notice, for conduct that we believe violates these Terms or is harmful to other users, us, or third parties.</p>

        <h2>9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the Province of Alberta, Canada, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>

        <h2>10. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of our Services after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms. We will update the "last updated" date at the top of this page.</p>

        <h2>11. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these Terms? Contact us at <a href="mailto:eddie@mlebotics.com">eddie@mlebotics.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 760px;
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 6rem;
  }
  .legal__header { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .legal__header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }
  .legal__meta { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .legal__body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .legal__body p { font-size: .95rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.8; }
  .legal__body h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: .5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .legal__body ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .4rem;
  }
  .legal__body li { font-size: .95rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.7; }
  .legal__body a { color: var(--cyan); text-decoration: none; }
  .legal__body a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .legal__body strong { color: #e2e8f0; }
</style>
